#MOBILE
Vnum       14500
Keywords   leper gnome irradiated crazed~
Short      a Crazed Leper Gnome~
Long       A Crazed Leper Gnome twitches and gibbers, radiation burns covering its body.
~
Desc       Once a proud citizen of Gnomeregan, this gnome has been driven mad by
radiation exposure. Its skin is mottled green and peeling, its eyes glow
with sickly light, and it attacks anything that moves with mindless fury.
Patches of hair have fallen out, and its movements are jerky and unpredictable.
~
Race       gnome~
Class      warrior~
Position   standing~
DefPos     standing~
Gender     neuter~
Actflags   npc aggressive stayarea~
