Keywords   leper gnome technician irradiated~
Short      a Leper Gnome Technician~
Long       A Leper Gnome Technician fumbles with sparking wires, cackling madly.
~
Desc       This leper gnome retains some memory of its former profession, though its
mind is shattered. It tinkers obsessively with broken machinery, creating
dangerous contraptions that spark and smoke. Its fingers are burned from
constant electrical shocks, but it doesn't seem to notice or care.
~
